title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 30 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Sep 30 2022
description:
Putin's annexing of four territories in Ukraine, threatens to use nuclear weapons. Biden pledges more money for Ukraine, says Putin won't get away with it, warns Putin not to attack NATO territory. Biden says Putin's lying on Nord Stream pipeline sabotage. Is there a plan to diffuse this powder keg? Stephen Miller on Biden's cognitive impairment. Ainsley Earhardt of Fox & Friends joins Clay and Buck to talk about her new children's book, I'm So Glad You Were Born. C&B end the week with some good news. Good polling news to end the week.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
